<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Enquiry Received</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; color: #333;">
  <p>Dear {{ customer.name }},</p>

  <p>Thank you for your enquiry. We've received your request and will be in touch within 1–2 business days.</p>

  {% if enquiry.hireStartDate %}
    <p>You requested items for: <strong>{{ enquiry.hireStartDate | dateFormat('short') }}{% if enquiry.hireEndDate %} – {{ enquiry.hireEndDate | dateFormat('short') }}{% endif %}</strong></p>
  {% endif %}

  {% if enquiry.venueName %}
    <p>Venue: <strong>{{ enquiry.venueName }}</strong></p>
  {% endif %}

  <p>If you have any questions in the meantime, please don't hesitate to get in touch:</p>
  <p>
    📧 <a href="mailto:{{ companySettings.contactEmail }}">{{ companySettings.contactEmail }}</a><br>
    📞 {{ companySettings.contactPhone }}
  </p>

  <p>Kind regards,<br>{{ companySettings.companyName }}</p>
</body>
</html>
